# husky-pre-commit
# Husky pre-commit hook for trustlock dependency admission checks.
# Use this when: your project uses Husky for Git hook management.
#
# To use:
#   1. Copy this file to .husky/pre-commit in your project root.
#   2. Make it executable: chmod +x .husky/pre-commit
#   3. Ensure Husky is initialized: npx husky install
#
# Advisory mode: warns on blocked packages but does not block the commit.
# To block commits on violations, add --enforce to the command below.

trustlock check
